# NBE Portal — maintenance client access

- Approved **single** reports use `share_token` and client viewer at `/report/view/[token]` (same page resolves merged or single).
- **Copy client link** must copy the **viewer URL** from `maintenanceReportClientViewUrl` / `client_view_url` (`NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` + `/report/view/{share_token}`), not `pdf_url` (Supabase PDF file URL).
- Merged rows store the viewer URL in `merged_reports.pdf_url`; single rows expose `client_view_url` on `GET /api/maintenance/reports` and on draft/approve responses.
- Portal **Download** uses `GET /api/maintenance/pdf/[reportId]`; embed `coverQrPngBytes` when `status === 'approved'`, `approved === true`, and `share_token` is set.
- Apply DB migration `047_maintenance_reports_client_share` before relying on `share_token` / `approved` columns.
